'''地球物理研究期刊'''（''Journal of Geophysical Research'', JGR）是由[[美國地球物理聯盟|美國地球物理聯盟]]出版的[[同行評審|同行評審]]地球物理學期刊，一年出版80期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/pubs/journals/|title=Journal of Geophysical Research homepage|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2011-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923193117/http://www.agu.org/pubs/journals/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該期刊包含與地球、太陽、太陽系相關的物理學、化學、生物學過程相關研究。該期刊分成七個部分：A (Space Physics), B (Solid Earth), C (Oceans), D (Atmospheres), E (Planets), F (Earth Surface), and G (Biogeosciences)。使用者可在線上獲得所有現期和過期期刊。

==歷史==
地球物理研究期刊於1896年創刊時，美國地球物理聯盟的會長{{Link-en|路易士·阿格里可拉·鮑爾|Louis Agricola Bauer}}命名為 ''Terrestrial Magnetism''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/journals/tm/1890.shtml|title=Terrestrial Magnetism Volumes 1(1896)–3(1898)|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314233037/http://www.agu.org/journals/tm/1890.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1899年到1948年期間名稱為 ''Terrestrial Magnetism and Atmospheric Electricity''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/journals/te/1900.shtml|title=Terrestrial Magnetism and Atmospheric Electricity Volumes 4 (1899)–14 (1909)|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314181831/http://www.agu.org/journals/te/1900.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1980年建立了三個部分：''A: Space Physics'', ''B: Solid Earth'', and ''C: Oceans''<ref name=jgr1980>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/1980.shtml|title=Journal of Geophysical Research Volumes 85 (1980)–94 (1989)|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606115828/http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/1980.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後再建立四個部分：1984年建立 ''D: Atmospheres''<ref name=jgr1980/>、1991年建立 ''E: Planets''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/1990.shtml|title=Journal of Geophysical Research Volumes 95 (1990)–104 (1999)|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606120338/http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/1990.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>、2003年建立 ''F: Earth Surface''<ref name=jgr2000>{{cite web|url=http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/2000.shtml|title=Journal of Geophysical Research Volumes 105 (2000)–114 (2009)|work=American Geophysical Union|accessdate=July 2011|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606101925/http://www.agu.org/journals/jgr/2000.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及2005年建立的 ''G: Biogeosciences''<ref name=jgr2000/>。

